title: Break plus - Outdoor-Wall lamps
description: The Break Plus wall lamp converts any surface into a three-dimensional mural. Arranged individually or as a group, it consists of a range of cubic and cylindrical volumes that cast diffuse, indirect light upwards, downwards, or in both directions. Surface mounted and easily maintained, the Break Plus outdoor lamp is suitable for both private residential properties as well as larger commercial projects, its lacquered matte finish adding a hint of graininess that complements its geometric form
